## Bottom Navigation & Tabs

- **Order**: Profile → Discover → Properties → Liked → Visits.
- **Implementation**
  - Primary widget: [lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar_new.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar_new.dart). If not present, fallback to [lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart).
  - Center tab routes to the main swipe interface (Home/Properties module).
- **Routes**
  - Ensure each tab maps to a named route defined in [lib/app/routes/app_routes.dart](mdc:lib/app/routes/app_routes.dart) and page in [lib/app/routes/app_pages.dart](mdc:lib/app/routes/app_pages.dart).
- **Consistency**
  - Tabs available across primary screens. Do not add ad-hoc nav bars per view.
- **Accessibility**
  - Ensure labels are localized (`.tr`) and meet contrast/tap target guidelines.